ol:Journalism|voy=no|d=no|species=no|s=no|commons=Category:Journalism|wikt=journalism|n=Category:Journalism}}\n* {{Curlie|News/Journalism/Organizations}}\n* [http://www.ojr.org ''Online Journalism Review'']\n=== Journalism organizations ===\n{{linkfarm|section|date=March 2020}}\n{{cmn|colwidth=25em|\n* [http://www.aim.org Accuracy in Media]\n* [http://www.iwmf.org African Women\u2019s Media Center]\n* [http://www.airmedia.org Association of Independents in Radio (AIR)]\n* [http://www.aasfe.org American Association of Sunday and Features Editors]\n* [http://www.copydesk.org American Copy Editors Society]\n* [http://www.afrta.org American Federation of Radio and Television Artists]\n* [http://www.ajr.org American Journalism Review]\n* [http://www.amwa.org American Medical Writers Association]\n* [http://www.anwc.org American News Women\u2019s Club]\n* [http://www.americanpressinstitute.org American Press Institute]\n* [http://www.asbpe.org American Society of Business Publication Editors]\n* [http://www.asja.org American Society of Journalists and Authors]\n* [http://www.asne.org American Society of Newspaper Editors]\n* [http://www.awrt.org American Women in Radio and Television]\n* [http://www.aspeninstitute.org Aspen Institute]\n* [http://www.apme.org Associated Press Managing Editors]\n* [http://www.apphotomanagers.org Associated Press Photo Managers]\n* [http://www.apsportseditors.org Associated Press Sports Editors]\n* [http://www.womencomm.org Association for Women in Communications]\n* [http://www.awsmonline.org Association for Women in Sports Media]\n* [http://www.awjchicago.org Association for Women Journalists]\n* [http://www.aan.org Association of Alternative Newsmedia]\n* [http://www.editorialcartoonists.com Association of American Editorial Cartoonists]\n* [http://www.capitolbeat.org Association of Capitol Reporters and Editors]\n* [http://www.afjonline.org Association of Food Journalists]\n* [http://www.healthjournalism.org Association of Health Care Jo